HEADWORD: Peanut butter
<hw>Pea"nut but"ter</hw>. <def>A paste made by mixing ground fresh
roasted peanuts with a small quantity of water or oil, and used chiefly
as a relish on sandwiches, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

